node.text: Derek’s “In and Of Itself,” on Hulu blew me away. He’s an amazing illusionist and performer who explores paradigm shifting observations on identity in what I believe is the most original and inventive show of the year.

node.text: For every human need met by an act of humble service, we stitch an invisible thread into the tattered fabric of our American society. Nothing feels better. I promise you. We can emerge from this dark season more connected than before. Be cautious with that which you share. Are you sewing or tearing?

node.text:
CONGRATULATIONS! YOU DID IT! You have made @thetomorrowwar a HOME RUN win!

Happy 4th of July!!

Thank YOU to everyone who watched The Tomorrow War this weekend. The first 48 hours of global viewing for The Tomorrow War on Prime Video broke all the records🙏🏻🙏🏻❤️❤️💪🏼💪🏼. #1 streaming film in the world!! And we could not have done that without each and everyone of you. Thank you all for joining us on this adventure! Happy 4th!!
